afford to raise him here.

77
00:07:13,862 --> 00:07:16,482
Look, maybe one day,
we'll beat the system.

78
00:07:16,551 --> 00:07:20,379
But right now, the safest place
for you to be is Europe.

79
00:07:20,448 --> 00:07:23,137
