91
00:08:28,310 --> 00:08:32,689
'Location 1709,
Martin Luther King Boulevard.'

92
00:08:32,758 --> 00:08:35,896
Terminate with extreme
prejudice. End.

93
00:08:36,827 --> 00:08:39,241
