temporary capsule.

100
00:09:13,103 --> 00:09:16,172
The European artificial womb
is on the boat.

101
00:09:16,241 --> 00:09:18,241
If the fetus gets to it
on time

102
00:09:18,310 --> 00:09:20,689
it can develop
there safely until birth.

103
00:09:20,758 --> 00:09:23,241
Until then, Mary will be feeding
him every few hours.

104
00:09:23,310 --> 00:09:25,275
'Is everyone clear
on the route?'

105
00:09:25,344 --> 00:09:28,931
The course has been clouded
to avoid the danger zones.

106
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:31,793
These three areas
are unsafe now.

107
00:09:31,862 --> 00:09:34,896
'During burn time tomorrow,
we'll go underground'.

108
00:09:34,965 --> 00:09:37,448
I have also set
an alternate course here

109
00:09:37,517 --> 00:09:39,448
in case of
unforeseen difficulties.

110
00:09:39,517 --> 00:09:43,931
- Like the Cyborg patrol.
- Like anything that comes up.

111
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:46,379
What about the Ozzie
blocker tablets?

112
00:09:49,413 --> 00:09:53,344
These are only a blocking agent
against radio activity.

113
00:09:53,413 --> 00:09:57,034
Ideally, you've gotta avoid
all contaminated substances.

114
00:09:57,103 --> 00:09:58,620
- Dr. Buckley.
- What is it?

115
00:09:58,689 --> 00:10:00,275
'We got a problem'.

116
00:10:03,758 --> 00:10:06,517
What the hell's
wrong with this?

117
00:10:06,586 --> 00:10:08,620
'Something's overridden our
security directive.'

118
00:10:08,689 --> 00:10:11,172
It's the system,
there's no doubt about it.

119
00:10:11,241 --> 00:10:13,413
They probably tapped
into your damn modem.

120
00:10:13,482 --> 00:10:15,965
