121
00:10:16,034 --> 00:10:17,068
[Mary]
'Take cover.'

122
00:10:17,137 --> 00:10:19,724
[screaming]

123
00:10:19,793 --> 00:10:21,724
'Quick, get the fetus
outta here, now.'

