170
00:19:50,896 --> 00:19:53,517
- Some competition.
- Oh, yes.

171
00:19:53,586 --> 00:19:55,758
Hmm, you can keep..

172
00:19:55,827 --> 00:19:58,172
Heavens be praised.

173
00:19:58,241 --> 00:20:01,586
God's are smiling
down on me tonight.

174
00:20:01,655 --> 00:20:04,379
