Really?
Is that so?

177
00:20:10,206 --> 00:20:12,241
[all laughing]

178
00:20:13,586 --> 00:20:15,586
Well I think
the smart thing to do

179
00:20:15,655 --> 00:20:18,827
is to have a look
inside your nifty bag here.

180
00:20:18,896 --> 00:20:21,103
I wouldn't be surprised if you
were hiding something

181
00:20:21,172 --> 00:20:23,827
- really yummy in there.
- Hm. Yummy, yummy.

182
00:20:23,896 --> 00:20:25,448
[groaning]

183
00:20:26,620 --> 00:20:28,724
[groaning]

184
00:20:33,034 --> 00:20:35,827
[dramatic music]

185
00:20:43,241 --> 00:20:45,172
[music continues]

186
00:20:52,379 --> 00:20:53,689
Argh.

187
00:21:15,310 --> 00:21:17,793
