You wanna talk?

188
00:21:17,862 --> 00:21:20,344
What's my other choice, asshole?

189
00:21:24,068 --> 00:21:26,000
Shut up.

190
00:21:43,344 --> 00:21:45,137
Who are you?

191
00:21:47,724 --> 00:21:49,689
Nobody in particular.

192
00:21:49,758 --> 00:21:52,137
Just taking back
what's rightfully mine.

193
00:21:56,137 --> 00:21:58,172
You got a problem with that?

194
00:22:01,482 --> 00:22:03,586
- Excuse me.
- What?

195
00:22:03,655 --> 00:22:06,896
I was wondering if you could
show me the way to the port.

196
00:22:06,965 --> 00:22:09,000
