01:26:15,724 --> 01:26:17,000
[groaning]

803
01:26:22,689 --> 01:26:24,586
[techno music]

804
01:26:39,482 --> 01:26:40,793
[explosion]

805
01:26:40,862 --> 01:26:42,827
No!

806
01:26:48,275 --> 01:26:49,931
[beeping]

807
01:26:52,724 --> 01:26:54,758
Austin, the baby!

808
01:26:54,827 --> 01:26:56,103
'Hurry!'

809
01:27:03,137 --> 01:27:04,310
[speaking French]

810
01:27:22,068 --> 01:27:23,793
Ah.

811
01:27:24,413 --> 01:27:25,344
[gasping]

812
01:27:28,448 --> 01:27:29,965
[speaking French]

813
01:27:44,482 --> 01:27:46,172
[dramatic music]

814
01:28:02,758 --> 01:28:05,206
[male speaking French]

815
01:28:08,172 --> 01:28:09,172
[male #1]
Oh!

816
01:28:17,172 --> 01:28:18,724
It's okay.

817
01:28:21,517 --> 01:28:23,000
[speaking French]

818
01:28:39,103 --> 01:28:40,620
Austin!

819
01:28:49,310 --> 01:28:50,655
I'm sorry.

820
01:28:51,655 --> 01:28:53,931
I was just
so scared and confused.

821
01:28:54,000 --> 01:28:56,965
It's okay. I know.

822
01:28:57,034 --> 01:28:59,172
I didn't know either.

823
01:29:01,000 --> 01:29:03,000
They must've screwed up
when they made me.

824
01:29:04,379 --> 01:29:08,172
Imagine a machine
feeling compassion for humans.

825
01:29:09,206 --> 01:29:10,241
Come with me.

826
01:29:11,551 --> 01:29:12,965
I can't.

827
01:29:13,034 --> 01:29:15,448
The baby's gonna need a father.

828
01:29:15,517 --> 01:29:17,448
He'll have a great mother.

829
01:29:19,379 --> 01:29:21,000
Please, Austin.

830
01:29:22,241 --> 01:29:24,793
We both have a job to do.

831
01:29:24,862 --> 01:29:28,551
I know the system.
I can beat them.

832
01:29:28,620 --> 01:29:31,000
All those people back
in the city need hope.

833
01:29:33,000 --> 01:29:34,931
I can be their hope.

834
01:29:38,551 --> 01:29:41,931
I'm gonna name the baby Austin.

835
01:29:42,000 --> 01:29:45,344
And as he grows up, I'm gonna
tell him all about you.

836
01:29:47,965 --> 01:29:50,068
Goodbye, Mary.

837
01:30:03,586 --> 01:30:06,000
[men speaking French]

838
01:30:25,896 --> 01:30:27,620
[instrumental music]

839
01:30:35,344 --> 01:30:37,517
[boat engine revving]

840
01:30:47,896 --> 01:30:50,103
[music continues]

841
01:31:07,758 --> 01:31:10,689
[eerie music]

